Reference

Model-Implied Matrices

Model-implied matrices for the k-variable linear regression model.

Sigmatheta()

Model-Implied Variance-Covariance Matrix \(\boldsymbol{\Sigma} \left( \boldsymbol{\theta} \right)\)

mutheta()

Model-Implied Mean Vector \(\boldsymbol{\mu} \left( \boldsymbol{\theta} \right)\)

Regression Coefficients and Error Variance

Regression coefficients and error variance from model-implied matrices.

intercept()

Regression Intercept \(\beta_1\)

sigma2epsilon()

Error Variance \(\sigma^2\)

slopes()

Regression Slopes \(\boldsymbol{\beta}_{2 \cdots k}\)

slopesprime()

Regression Standardized Slopes \(\boldsymbol{\beta}_{2 \cdots k}^{*}\)

Regression Coefficients OLS.

Regression coefficients ordinary least squares estimator.

betahat()

Regression Coefficients \(\boldsymbol{\hat{\beta}}\)

betahatnorm()

Regression Coefficients \( \boldsymbol{\hat{\beta}} = \left( \mathbf{X}^{T} \mathbf{X} \right)^{-1} \left( \mathbf{X}^{T} \mathbf{y} \right) \)

betahatqr()

Regression Coefficients \(\boldsymbol{\hat{\beta}}\) - QR Decomposition

betahatsvd()

Regression Coefficients \(\boldsymbol{\hat{\beta}}\) - Singular Value Decomposition
